<br />

<br />
The answer is trivially simple.
<br />

<br />
How does each class solo in the later levels?
<br />

<br />
Mages : send in pet, heal and/or nuke.
<br />
Wizard : kiting
<br />
Druid : kiting
<br />
Enchanter : Charm
<br />
Bard : Swarm kiting
<br />
Shaman : Root-n-Rot
<br />
Necromancer : Root-n-Rot (snare/fear doesn't work at high levels, since level 55+ NPC are <span style="font-weight: bold">all</span> immune to fear) or agro-kiting
<br />
Shadowknight : Actually I am not sure on this one
<br />
Beastlord : Send in pet, heal and/or melee.
<br />

<br />
Which classes in that list solo by methods similar to that used by Mages? Beastlords. Nobody else.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: normal"><span style="color: red">Zyphyr Runnersbane</span></span>
